</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Prepare a detailed plan of how the funds you're applying for will be used.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section6-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=find-a-financial-backer>Find a financial backer.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-find-a-financial-backer-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Find a financial backer."></div></div><p>Find a <strong>venture capitalist, private equity investor, or angel investor</strong> to believe in your idea and provide the start-up funds for your production company. You can search online to find these investors, or attract them by means of a <strong>crowdfunding campaign.</strong></p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Comb through your <strong>professional and personal networks to find potential investors</strong>. Sometimes the person you're looking for could be a mutual friend.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section6-step5" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.5&nbsp;</span><h4 id=start-a-crowdfunding-campaign>Start a crowdfunding campaign.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-start-a-crowdfunding-campaign-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Start a crowdfunding campaign."></div></div><p>A crowdfunding campaign is a great way to generate the funds you need to start your production company. By constructing a compelling narrative around your production company, you can get strangers and <strong>angel investors</strong> to back your business and donate some start-up capital.</p><p><strong>Just be clear you've read the terms and conditions of the crowdfunding platform you're using.</strong></p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Make sure you've clearly outlined your own terms on your crowdfunding page and that potential investors know if there are any incentives for those who donate to your cause.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Set up <strong>social media pages</strong> related to your business so you can better engage with your audience. Maintain an active presence and try to respond to all questions.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Use your crowdfunding campaign to <strong>establish your client base</strong>. You are already attracting people who are interested in your business, so set up a mailing list and keep them updated on opening specials and more.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section6-step6" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.6&nbsp;</span><h4 id=use-your-own-savings>Use your own savings.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-use-your-own-savings-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Use your own savings."></div></div><p>Relying on personal savings to fund your start-up is a great way to <strong>remove debt from the equation</strong>, thereby reducing your risk when starting a new business.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section7" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>7.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=insure-your-production-company>Insure your production company.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section7-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-quotes-from-different-insurance-companies>Get quotes from different insurance companies.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-get-quotes-from-different-insurance-companies-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get quotes from different insurance companies."></div></div><p>Before committing to an insurance company, <strong>shop around and compare quotes and packages</strong>. Do your own research and make sure you are getting adequate coverage at the best price.</p><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p><strong>Find out about discounts.</strong> When you take out multiple policies from the same insurance provider or when you pay upfront, you may be eligible for a discount.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p><strong>Consult an independent agent.</strong> You can gain valuable insight by speaking to an independent insurance agent. Use their knowledge to help you make the final decision.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section7-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=purchase-insurance>Purchase insurance.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-purchase-insurance-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Purchase insurance."></div></div><p>Production projects are expensive, involving a range of valuable equipment and many people, and so you'll need to <strong>make sure you are covered project-to-project in case of unforeseen events</strong>.</p><p>Your production company should purchase several types of insurance, including:</p><ul><li>Media Liability Insurance.</li><li>Publisher's Perils Insurance.</li><li>Business interruption insurance.</li><li>Small Business Liability Insurance.</li><li>Commercial Auto Insurance.</li></ul><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Look for insurance companies that offer <strong>packages catering specifically for businesses in the media industry</strong>. These packages cover cast and crew, equipment, third party property damage, etc.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section8" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>8.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=decide-on-a-location>Decide on a location.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section8-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-your-office-requirements>Determine your office requirements.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-determine-your-office-requirements-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine your office requirements."></div></div><p>If you're running a small operation, and outsourcing much of the work that goes into getting a product out to market, anything more than a home office isn't really necessary. The size and the nature of your production company will determine the features of your office space.</p><p><strong>Some key questions to ask when determining your office requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>What will I be using this office for?</li><li>How many departments do I need?</li><li>How fast should my internet be?</li><li>How many staff members will work here?</li></ul></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section8-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=find-an-office>Find an office.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-find-an-office-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Find an office."></div></div><p>No matter the size of your production company, you'll need a location that's secure and safe, and one that is ideally situated near a transport hub.</p><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>If you're not ready to commit to a permanent location, look into <strong>shared office space</strong>. Co-working environments can be great for creative projects.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>To help keep your workers productive, happy, and healthy, consider investing in some basic gym equipment or having a dedicated recharge room or "chill space" where staff can unwind.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section9" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>9.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=hire-staff>Hire staff.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section9-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-how-many-workers-you-need>Determine how many workers you need.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-determine-how-many-workers-you-need-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine how many workers you need."></div></div><p>In the beginning, you'll play most of the roles found in the average production company, but you can start with a basic staff that will ensure your company gets off on the right foot.</p><p><strong>Basic staff:</strong></p><ul><li>Head of development.</li><li>Head of production.</li><li>Head of post-production.</li><li>Sales and distribution head.</li><li>Certified public accountant.</li></ul><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Be sure to factor in <strong>budgetary constraints</strong> when determining the size of your team.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section9-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=advertise-available-positions>Advertise available positions.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-advertise-available-positions-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Advertise available positions."></div></div><p>Write enticing job descriptions and post them on job sites, local job boards, social media. Be sure to use your professional networks to help spread the word as well.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section9-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=hire-employees-or-freelancers>Hire employees or freelancers.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-hire-employees-or-freelancers-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Hire employees or freelancers."></div></div><p><strong>For a small production company, it is best to build up a network of freelancers to tap into for each project.</strong> You can do that through platforms like <a
href="https://www.upwork.com/">Upwork</a>.</p><p><strong>For full-time staff you can use hiring software</strong> to help you streamline the process of posting jobs, accepting applications, scheduling interviews, and sending out final job offers.</p><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Always look for freelancers whose experience align with your project or the outlined job requirements.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>To protect your work, have your freelancers sign a legal document that states you are the owner of all completed work.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>To protect your clients, you may want freelancers to sign a <strong>non-compete agreement</strong>. This agreement essentially prevents them from stealing your clients.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section10" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>10.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=market-your-company>Market your company.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-production-company-section10-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-company-website>Create a company website.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-company-website-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create a company website."></div></div><p>Register a domain and build a site that explains who you are and what you offer, and that allows you to showcase your work. Having a website increases your <strong>visibility, discoverability, and legitimacy</strong>. Use a website builder to design a website or pay an expert to help you.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
