a.com/guides/how-to-start-a-production-company#how-to-start-a-production-company-section6-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-get-a-small-business-loan-from-the-bank-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p><strong>Do your research before meeting with the bank.<\/strong> If you are well-prepared, able to answer their questions directly and produce the relevant figures\/financial projections, you'll stand a better chance of securing your loan.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Be sure to send all the relevant information through to the bank in a timely manner.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Prepare a detailed plan of how the funds you're applying for will be used.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"4","name":"<p>Find a financial backer.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Find a <strong>venture capitalist, private equity investor, or angel investor<\/strong> to believe in your idea and provide the start-up funds for your production company. You can search online to find these investors, or attract them by means of a <strong>crowdfunding campaign.<\/strong><\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-production-company#how-to-start-a-production-company-section6-step4","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-find-a-financial-backer-288x288-20200820.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Comb through your <strong>professional and personal networks to find potential investors<\/strong>. Sometimes the person you're looking for could be a mutual friend.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"5","name":"<p>Start a crowdfunding campaign.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>A crowdfunding campaign is a great way to generate the funds you need to start your production company. By constructing a compelling narrative